      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さん、凄く美味しそうに食べるな",
      "startTime": 8.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ここからは、さっき録音したナレーションを流しながら\n食べるんですよね？",
      "startTime": 15.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "次はさくらんぼプリンを食べて……\n最後はさくらんぼをそのまま一口、ですね",
      "startTime": 20.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、よろしくお願いします！",
      "startTime": 24.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "んふー！　美味しー！",
      "startTime": 29.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（奥山さんが満面の笑みを浮かべて食べている間に）\n（別録りしたナレーションが流れ始めた）",
      "startTime": 37.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "「このお仕事を始めてから\n大変なことは沢山ありました」",
      "startTime": 43.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "「でも、それ以上に……得たものがいっぱいあります」",
      "startTime": 46.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "「楽しんで、落ち込んで、成長して……\n全部繋がって、今の私がある」",
      "startTime": 56.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "「このさくらんぼが生まれるまでの歴史を知った時\n私はどこか、自分に重なるところを感じたんです」",
      "startTime": 64.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さんが考えたナレーション、凄くいいな\n周りのみなさんも聞き入ってる",
      "startTime": 74.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、山形のさくらんぼは美味しいな",
      "startTime": 77.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "バッチリですか！？　ありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 83.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（奥山さんのああいう大人っぽい喋りは、ギャップが）\n（あって素敵だな。仕事の参考にさせてもらおう）",
      "startTime": 90.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さーん？　あれ、外で休憩かな？",
      "startTime": 97.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "も～、引っ張っちゃダメだよ～！",
      "startTime": 104.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "こらー、待ちなさーい！",
      "startTime": 108.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "地元の子供達か。本当に人気者だな",
      "startTime": 110.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そろそろ行かないと\nふふ、大丈夫だよ。またいつでも遊んであげるから！",
      "startTime": 118.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "約束だからね。はい、ゆーびきーりげーんまーん\nうそついたらはりせんぼんのーます、ゆーびきった！",
      "startTime": 127.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、次遊ぶ時までいい子にしてるんだよ？",
      "startTime": 134.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（CMは大人っぽかったけど、今はお姉さんって感じだ）\n（奥山さんのこういう姿、新鮮だな）",
      "startTime": 144.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（事務所では妹分だし、普段気付かない一面を）\n（引き出せるように、俺もまだまだ頑張らなきゃな）",
      "startTime": 151.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5300.000000000011,
          "startTime": 156.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん。{user}さん\n大変なことになってるんです！　どうしましょー！",
      "startTime": 159.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "落ち着いてくれ、何があったんだ？",
      "startTime": 163.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "この間のCM、ローカルCMだけど凄く話題になって\n動画サイトに投稿することになったんです……",
      "startTime": 171.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺もその動画を観たけど、かなり再生されてたな\n急上昇ランキングにも入ってたし",
      "startTime": 179.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなんです！　いくら素敵なCMとはいえ\nさすがに広がり過ぎじゃないかって慌てちゃいました",
      "startTime": 186.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも、このCMが流れて\n凄くいいことがあったんです！",
      "startTime": 193.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "私のナレーションを聞いた学校の友達が\n「いくら断られても、めげずに遊びに誘うから！」って",
      "startTime": 199.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_03-smr022.m4a",
      "text": "誘ってほしいけど、断るのも申し訳なかったから……\nあんな風に言ってもらえて、本当に嬉しかったです",
      "startTime": 208.8333333333,
